	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino, charissime Bullingere.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saxonicas ecclesias pessimo esse in statu cum ob bellum crudele tum ob adiaphora melius nosti ex literis, quas <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8101">Lęlius</persName> ad te misit, quam ego, etsi parum hac de re scripsit d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8490">Valentinus Pacęus</persName>, contionator Lipsensis; tu certiora velis communicare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Lantzknechtius</persName> quidam ad nos venit, qui spargit exercitum d. ab <persName ref="p8034" cert="high">Heideck</persName> dispersum et partim a <persName ref="p18250" cert="high">Mauritio</persName> susceptum, partim elapsum in varias regiones et iam conari alium colligere, sed nervos belli<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Vgl. <hi>Cicero,</hi> Orationes Philippicae, 5, 5 und s. <bibl>HBBW</bibl> XIV *** .</note> deesse.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Magdeburgenses</placeName> summo in periculo sunt, urgentur ab hostibus, ut nesciant, quo se vertant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum expecto a te literas, quę certiora et fortassis feliciora indicabunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconius</persName> noster lecto affixus est, ac nihil edit, sed perpetuo bibit; nequit enim sitim extinguere; senex est, et natura deficit in horas, vix recuperabit sanitatem pristinam, etsi domino omnia possibilia sint.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale et rescribe.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">18. februarii 1551.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis meo nomine d. <persName type="auto_name">Theodorum</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi plura.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name">Schertlinus</persName> abiit, bonus vir et pius... Eximio viro d. Heinrycho Bullingero, concionatori apud Tigurinam ecclesiam diligentissimo, praeceptori suo charissimo.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
